parameters.name: $src_straight_through_processing_data_staging$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT 
ds_left.left_straight_through_processing_data_staging_id,
ds_left.left_straight_through_processing_validated_data_source_system as stp_validated_data_source_system,
'Straight Through Processing' AS stp_validated_data_domain,
ds_left.left_straight_through_processing_validated_data_type AS stp_validated_data_type,
GETDATE() AS stp_validated_data_row_effective_start_datetime,
'9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000' AS stp_validated_data_row_effective_end_datetime,
'Loaded' AS stp_validated_data_load_state,
ds_left.left_originating_source_name,
ds_left.left_originating_load_type,
ds_left.left_straight_through_processing_validated_data_row_source_system_key,
ds_left.left_policy_source_system_id,
ds_left.left_policy_number,
ds_left.left_policy_module_number,
ds_left.left_line_of_business,
ds_left.left_policy_effective_date,
ds_left.left_risk_id,
ds_left.left_risk_state,
ds_left.left_insured_name,
ds_left.left_customer_number,
ds_left.left_transaction_code,
ds_left.left_transaction_datetime,
ds_left.left_user_type_code,
ds_left.left_source_schema_name,
ds_left.left_source_table_name,
ds_left.left_source_field_name,
case 
	when ds_left.left_source_field_name ='birthdt'  and ds_left.left_source_value <> 'NULL' then cast(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM SYSDATE) - LEFT(ds_left.left_source_value, 4) as varchar)
    when ds_left.left_source_field_name ='building_number_of_dangerous_trees' and (ds_left.left_source_value is null or ds_left.left_source_value ='NULL') then '0' 
    when ds_left.left_source_field_name ='limit_coverage_limit1' and (ds_left.left_source_value is null or ds_left.left_source_value ='NULL') then '0' 
	else ds_left.left_source_value 
	end as left_source_value,
ds_right.right_straight_through_processing_data_staging_id,
ds_right.right_originating_source_name,
ds_right.right_originating_load_type,
ds_right.right_straight_through_processing_validated_data_row_source_system_key,
ds_right.right_source_schema_name,
ds_right.right_source_table_name,
ds_right.right_source_field_name,
ds_right.right_source_value,
ds_left.left_straight_through_processing_rule_row_id,
ds_left.rule_id,
ds_left.rule_type,
ds_left.rule_name,
ds_left.condition_group_number,
ds_left.condition_order_number,
ds_left.condition_column_name_left,
ds_left.calculation_operator,
ds_right.condition_column_name_right,
ds_left.calculation_operator as calculation_operator,
ds_left.calculation_constant_value,
ds_left.comparative_operator,
ds_left.comparative_type,
ds_left.threshold_value,
ds_left.logical_operator,
ds_left.action_flag,
ds_left.priority_order_number,
cb.batch_id as batch_id
FROM 
(
  select
    ds1.straight_through_processing_data_staging_id AS left_straight_through_processing_data_staging_id,
    ds1.straight_through_processing_data_staging_source_system AS left_straight_through_processing_validated_data_source_system,
    ds1.straight_through_processing_data_staging_type AS left_straight_through_processing_validated_data_type,
    ds1.originating_source_name AS left_originating_source_name,
    ds1.originating_load_type AS left_originating_load_type,
    ds1.straight_through_processing_data_staging_row_source_system_key AS left_straight_through_processing_validated_data_row_source_system_key,
    ds1.policy_source_system_id AS left_policy_source_system_id,
    ds1.policy_number AS left_policy_number,
    ds1.policy_module_number AS left_policy_module_number,
    ds1.line_of_business AS left_line_of_business,
    ds1.policy_effective_date AS left_policy_effective_date,
    ds1.risk_id AS left_risk_id,
    ds1.risk_state AS left_risk_state,
    ds1.insured_name AS left_insured_name,
    ds1.customer_number AS left_customer_number,
    ds1.transaction_code AS left_transaction_code,
    ds1.transaction_datetime AS left_transaction_datetime,
    ds1.user_type_code AS left_user_type_code,
    ds1.source_schema_name AS left_source_schema_name,
    ds1.source_table_name AS left_source_table_name,
    ds1.source_field_name AS left_source_field_name,
    ds1.source_value AS left_source_value,
    r1.straight_through_processing_rule_row_id as left_straight_through_processing_rule_row_id,
    r1.rule_id,
    r1.rule_type,
    r1.rule_name,
    r1.condition_group_number,
    r1.condition_order_number,
    r1.condition_schema_name_left,
    r1.condition_object_name_left,
    r1.condition_column_name_left,
    r1.calculation_operator,
    r1.calculation_constant_value,
    r1.comparative_operator,
    r1.comparative_type,
    r1.threshold_value,
    r1.logical_operator,
    r1.action_flag,
    r1.priority_order_number
  FROM $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_data_staging ds1
  JOIN $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules r1 
  ON ds1.source_schema_name = r1.condition_schema_name_left
  AND ds1.source_table_name = r1.condition_object_name_left
  AND ds1.source_field_name = r1.condition_column_name_left
  and  r1.straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
  ) ds_left
LEFT JOIN 
(
  SELECT
    ds2.straight_through_processing_data_staging_id AS right_straight_through_processing_data_staging_id,
    ds2.straight_through_processing_data_staging_source_system AS right_straight_through_processing_validated_data_source_system,
    ds2.straight_through_processing_data_staging_type AS right_straight_through_processing_validated_data_type,
    ds2.originating_source_name AS right_originating_source_name,
    ds2.originating_load_type AS right_originating_load_type,
    ds2.straight_through_processing_data_staging_row_source_system_key AS right_straight_through_processing_validated_data_row_source_system_key,
    ds2.policy_source_system_id AS right_policy_source_system_id,
    ds2.policy_number AS right_policy_number,
    ds2.policy_module_number AS right_policy_module_number,
    ds2.line_of_business AS right_line_of_business,
    ds2.policy_effective_date AS right_policy_effective_date,
    ds2.risk_id AS right_risk_id,
    ds2.risk_state AS right_risk_state,
    ds2.insured_name AS right_insured_name,
    ds2.customer_number AS right_customer_number,
    ds2.transaction_code AS right_transaction_code,
    ds2.transaction_datetime AS right_transaction_datetime,
    ds2.user_type_code AS right_user_type_code,
    ds2.source_schema_name AS right_source_schema_name,
    ds2.source_table_name AS right_source_table_name,
    ds2.source_field_name AS right_source_field_name,
    ds2.source_value AS right_source_value,
    r2.straight_through_processing_rule_row_id AS right_straight_through_processing_rule_row_id,
    r2.condition_schema_name_right,
    r2.condition_object_name_right,
    r2.condition_column_name_right
  FROM $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_data_staging ds2
  JOIN $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules  r2
  ON ds2.source_schema_name = r2.condition_schema_name_right
  AND ds2.source_table_name = r2.condition_object_name_right
  AND ds2.source_field_name = r2.condition_column_name_right
  and r2.straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
) ds_right
ON ds_left.left_straight_through_processing_rule_row_id = ds_right.right_straight_through_processing_rule_row_id
AND ds_left.left_policy_source_system_id = ds_right.right_policy_source_system_id
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
left join $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data vd
on ds_left.left_policy_number = vd.policy_number and ds_left.left_policy_source_system_id = vd.policy_source_system_id 
and vd.stp_validated_data_row_effective_end_datetime ='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
where 1=1  
and ds_left.left_risk_state in ($$state_list) and ds_left.left_line_of_business ='$$line_of_business' --added this as part of the pilot
and (vd.policy_number is null or ds_left.left_transaction_datetime > vd.transaction_datetime )
order by ds_left.left_policy_number, ds_left.left_policy_number, cast(substring(ds_left.rule_id, 2) as int), ds_left.condition_order_number;

parameters.name: $lkp_straight_through_processing_rules$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
select Rule_ID, count(*) as Rule_ID_Count from $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules
where straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
group by Rule_ID
order by cast(substring(rule_id, 2) as int)

parameters.name: $lkp_straight_through_processing_rules_3_Calculation_operator$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
select Rule_ID, calculation_operator as rule_calculation_operator  from $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules
where straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000' and condition_order_number =3
order by cast(substring(rule_id, 2) as int)

parameters.name: $lkp_straight_through_processing_rules_calculation_constant_value$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
select Rule_ID, condition_order_number, calculation_constant_value   from $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules
where straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
order by cast(substring(rule_id, 2) as int)

parameters.name: $lkp_straight_through_processing_rules_condition_column_left$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
select Rule_ID, condition_order_number, condition_column_name_left  from $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules
where straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
order by cast(substring(rule_id, 2) as int)
